iven name has always been popular throughout Christendom, in part because St Thomas's doubts have made him seem a very human character."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Thomas Lound was born in 1165, in Cheshire, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 daughter. He died in Somme, Picardie, France."},"et":{"1165–":"1165–Surnud","1200–1293":"1200–1293","1165–Male":"1165–Surnud","1200":"1200","1165":"1165","1293":"1293","Somme, Picardie, France":"Somme, Picardie, Prantsusmaa","Culton, Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1165–":"1165–Kuollut","1200–1293":"1200–1293","1165–Male":"1165–Kuollut","1200":"1200","1165":"1165","1293":"1293","Somme, Picardie, France":"Somme, Picardie, Ranska","Culton, Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1165–":"1165–Décédé","1200–1293":"1200–1293","1165–Male":"1165–Décédé","1200":"1200","1165":"1165","1293":"1293","Somme, Picardie, France":"Somme, Picardie, France","Culton, Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Thomas Lound est né en 1165, à Cheshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fille. Il est décédé à Somme, Picardie, France."},"de":{"1165–":"1165–Verstorben","1200–1293":"1200–1293","1165–Male":"1165–Verstorben","1200":"1200","1165":"1165","1293":"1293","Somme, Picardie, France":"Somme, Picardie, Frankreich","Culton, Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Thomas Lound wurde 1165 in Cheshire, England, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Tochter. Er starb in Somme, Picardie, Frankreich."},"ht":{"1165–":"1165–Desede","1200–1293":"1200–1293","1165–Male":"1165–Desede","1200":"1200","1165":"1165","1293":"1293","Somme, Picardie, France":"Somme, Picardie, France","Culton, Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1165–":"1165–elhunyt","1200–1293":"1200–1293","1165–Male":"1165–elhunyt","1200":"1200","1165":"1165","1293":"1293","Somme, Picardie, France":"Somme, Picardie, Franci